data.description: Highly sought after OVERLOOK of Lilydale.  Enter into the captivating great room with spectacular fireplace.  Sunrooms flank both sides of living room.  Oversized primary bedroom with two closets (one a walk-in).  Private bath accents bedroom.  Second bedroom is spacious - perfect for visitors, home office, den.  You'll enjoy the indoor heated pool, party room w/kitchen & deck, exercise room, tennis courts.  All with spectacular views of the manicured grounds surrounded by trees and wildlife.  The seller has had thirty years of enjoyment and looks forward to a new owner having the same.
